	•	5 terrain tiles (basin/saddle/ridge/canyon/tube)
	•	For each: sensors, gates, remediations, artifacts, owner daemon
	•	Plus a “when under attack” quick sequence (Hound→Mirror→Ghost→Dragonfly→Checksum→Duck).